@node African
@{FG HIGHLIGHT}Name@{FG TEXT}            : Chief Gcaleka
@{FG HIGHLIGHT}Occupation@{FG TEXT}      : Tribesman 
@{FG HIGHLIGHT}Date of Birth@{FG TEXT}   : 29-12-70
@{FG HIGHLIGHT}Town/City@{FG TEXT}       : Xhosa
@{FG HIGHLIGHT}Country@{FG TEXT}         : South Africa
