particular, the things your 'colleagues' tend to say...


   The Manager :     "How hard can it be ?"
                     "That's crap.  Draw it again."
                     "You buy this round."

   The Programmer :  "Cool - I've found a major bug."
                     "I'll do it later."
                     "No."

